      <title>数据结构——树状数组</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/03/%E6%A0%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/03/%E6%A0%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="树状数组"><a href="#树状数组" class="headerlink" title="树状数组"></a>树状数组</h3><h4 id="1-对树状数组的基本了解"><a href="#1-对树状数组的基本了解" class="headerlink" title="1.对树状数组的基本了解"></a>1.对树状数组的基本了解</h4><p>树状数组，顾名思义就是用数组来模拟树形结构，主要用来解决大部分基于区间上的更新以及求和问题</p><p>优点是修改和查询的复杂度都是$$O(logN)$$，相比线段树系数要少很多，比传统数组要快，并且容易写</p><p>缺点是遇到复杂的区间问题还是不能解决，功能有限</p><h4 id="2-区间查询，单点更新"><a href="#2-区间查询，单点更新" class="headerlink" title="2.区间查询，单点更新"></a>2.区间查询，单点更新</h4><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P3374">P3374 【模板】树状数组 1</a></p><p>int getsum(int x){<br>    int sum &#x3D; 0;<br>    while (x &gt; 0){<br>        sum +&#x3D; c[x];<br>        x -&#x3D; lowbit(x);<br>    }<br>    return sum;<br>}</p><p>对于c[R]树状数组，R&#x3D;1~8来说，作图如下：</p><p><img src="/assets/blog_res/2022-11-03-%E6%A0%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/o_221101091413_%E6%A0%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE.png" alt="o_221101091413_树状数组图"></p><p>从图中可知，如果改变了 c[1] 的值，那么包含它的也要改变</p><p>如下：</p><p>c[1] –&gt; c[2] –&gt; c[4] –&gt; c[8]     1(0001)_2 –&gt; 2(0010)_2 –&gt; 4(0100)_2 –&gt; 8(1000)_2</p><p>c[3] –&gt; c[4] –&gt; c[8]     3(0011)_2 –&gt; 4(0100) –&gt; 8(1000)_2</p><p>从上面两个过程中我们可以看出，下标变化的规律是加上本身的<strong>lowbit()</strong></p><p>即如果改变的值的下标是 i，那么之后要改变的值的下标应该是这样的 </p><p>1 –&gt; 1+lowbit(1) –&gt; 1+lowbit(1)+lowbit(1+lowbit()) –&gt; · · ·</p><p>一直加到 n(数组的长度) 为止</p><p>写成代码如下</p><p>void update(int i, int k){<br>    while (i &lt;&#x3D; n){<br>        c[i] +&#x3D; k;<br>        i +&#x3D; lowbit(i);<br>    }<br>}</p><p>以上，我们就学会了树状数组的区间查询和单点更新</p><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P2880">P2880 USACO07JAN</a></p><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1908">P1908 逆序对</a></p><h4 id="3-单点查询，区间更新"><a href="#3-单点查询，区间更新" class="headerlink" title="3.单点查询，区间更新"></a>3.单点查询，区间更新</h4><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P3368">P3368 【模板】树状数组 2</a></p><p>如果题目要求是把 x~y 区间内的所有值全部加上 k 或者减去 k，然后查询某个点的值，这种时候应该怎么做呢</p><p>如果是像上面的树状数组来说，就必须把 x-y 区间内每个值都更新，这样的复杂度肯定是不行的，这个时候，就不能再用数据的值建树了</p><p>这里我们引入差分，利用差分建树</p><p>对于差分来说，会有一个差分数组 d 来储存原数组的差值</p><p>当某个区间[x,y]值改变了，区间内的差值是不变的，只有D[x]和D[y+1]的值发生改变</p><p>我们只需要更改两个值，就可以更新一个区间的值了</p><p>代码如下</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">lowbit</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x &amp; -x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">update</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> i, <span class="type">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (i &lt;= n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        c[i] += k;</span><br><span class="line">        i += <span class="built_in">lowbit</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">getsum</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> sum = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (x &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sum += c[x];</span><br><span class="line">        x -= <span class="built_in">lowbit</span>(x);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> sum;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">solve</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(i, a[i] - a[i - <span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(x, k);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(y + <span class="number">1</span>, -k);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> sum = <span class="built_in">getsum</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与区间查询，单点更新的区别就是初始化以及更新方式</p><p>[P5057 <a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P5057">CQOI2006</a></p><h4 id="4-区间更新，区间查询"><a href="#4-区间更新，区间查询" class="headerlink" title="4.区间更新，区间查询"></a>4.区间更新，区间查询</h4><blockquote><p>给出一个数列 ，你需要完成如下操作：</p></blockquote><ul><li><p>1:将区间[x, y]内每个数都加上 k;</p></li><li><p>2:输出区间[x, y]内每个数的和。</p></li></ul><p>上面我们说的差值建树状数组，得到的是某个点的值，那如果我既要区间更新，又要区间查询怎么办</p><p>这里我们还是利用差分，由上面可知</p><p>已知差分数组，求和sum</p><p>因此我们要维护两个树状数组，即用 d[i] 和 d[i]*(i-1) 来建树状数组</p><p>代码如下</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">lowbit</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> x &amp; -x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">update</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> i, <span class="type">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> x = i;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (i &lt;= n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        c1[i] += k;</span><br><span class="line">        c2[i] += k * (x - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        i += <span class="built_in">lowbit</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">getsum</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> sum = <span class="number">0</span>, i = x;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (x &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sum += i * c1[x] - c2[x];</span><br><span class="line">        x -= <span class="built_in">lowbit</span>(x);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> sum;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">solve</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(i, a[i] - a[i - <span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(x, k);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">update</span>(y + <span class="number">1</span>, -k);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> sum = <span class="built_in">getsum</span>(y) - <span class="built_in">geysum</span>(x - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
